These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill, pall-mall
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, grey, green
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who likes green##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage         | coffee | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | bongani    | dunhill      |
| Color     | grey     | ebony      | green |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, ship, scooter
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, march
City: edinburgh, rome, venice
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person eating kale is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person driving the ship and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Transport   | ship     | scooter     | trike      |
| Birthday   | march  | february | august |
| City           | venice | edinburgh     | rome       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, sunflower, begonia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, soul, jazz
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, taxi, subway
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person driving the tram is between the fan of jazz and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the taxi is the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person driving the tram is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Flower          | lily  | begonia     | sunflower     |
| Music-Genre           | jazz | r&b  | soul   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Transport           | subway     | tram | taxi |

