The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, ship, subway
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, argentine, mexican
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is between the person driving the ship and the russian##2
4. the havana-smoker is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar    | montecristo       | bolivar  | havana   |
| Transport     | ship    | subway  | bus |
| Nationality     | argentine   | mexican | russian        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

