.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
City: prague, miami, nizza
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, august
House: gothic-revival, victorian, ranch-style
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the gothic-revival house is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the victorian house##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City          | nizza    | prague     | miami      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Birthday   | august  | february       | march       |
| House           | victorian     | gothic-revival       | ranch-style     |

