.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
House: townhouse, futuristic, craftsman
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, coral, purple
City: nizza, san-francisco, venice
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the craftsman house is the person who likes red##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the futuristic house and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| House          | futuristic | townhouse | craftsman    |
| Color         | coral | purple      | red |
| City   | nizza   | san-francisco     | venice        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

