.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, musician, architect
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, badminton, snowboarding
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, november, june
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is between the architect and the person who's birthday is in march##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the musician##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Job          | architect      | musician   | librarian |
| Sport         | handball | badminton | snowboarding |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Birthday     | june         | november  | march       |

