2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | june      | may | january     |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks   | sudoku      | photography     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | horror      | musical |
