.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
City: prague, rome, miami
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, argentine
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, gospel
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the canadian is between the brazilian and the person traveling to rome##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the argentine##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the left of the brazilian##1
6. the fan of dubstep is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| City       | rome       | miami       | prague    |
| Nationality         | argentine | canadian | brazilian |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep        | gospel            | folk  |

