.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, grey, white
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, bird
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid, daisy
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growsorchid is in the middle##1
4. the person who growsorchid is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the hedgehog##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Color      | white     | grey | brown      |
| Pet         | chinchilla  | bird       | hedgehog |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Flower   | aconite | orchid    | daisy     |

