2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is between the person driving the subway and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Cigar      | pall-mall | aristoff      | baccarat            |
