There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, parkour, climbing
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Hobby           | skydiving   | card-games   | puzzles |
| Beverage   | juice | iced-tea   | milk     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Sport           | rugby | parkour | climbing    |

