.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, poker
There 3 different types of food: tomato, broccoli, asparagus
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, may
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the fan of disco is between the person playing bridge and the person eating tomato##2
4. the fan of reggae is the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person playing billiard and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Game      | bridge | poker     | billiard        |
| Food         | broccoli   | asparagus | tomato |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Birthday           | may           | september    | june       |

