.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, baking, chess
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, teacher, bartender
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
City: prague, new-york, liverpool
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the teacher is the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the bartender is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby        | baking      | collecting | chess |
| Job         | teacher     | bartender    | nurse        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| City   | prague          | new-york     | liverpool       |

 